Libraries
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Vorilon requires the use of several libraries and build tools.
Cmake v2.8: http://www.cmake.org/
Boost Libraries v1.42: http://www.boost.org/
Google Log v0.3.0: http://zi.fi/cmake/Modules/
Google Flags v1.1: http://code.google.com/p/google-gflags/

Build
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The proper way to build is an out of source build.  IE. /vorilon/build/
using cmake, if the libraries are not in the default installation path
they will have to be manually found and added.  Using static libraries
unless otherwise specified.